Ok this is kinda simple.

I rate it a 3/10 difficulty if your new at this stuff.

Files modifyed:

-class8.java
_________________________________________________________
I was going to add in a item dump but i couldn't find mine so here it goes. 

1.) First open up your class8.java in your clients folder.

2.) Search for [code]public static final Class8 method198(int i)[/code]

3.) Then somewhere near that text there will be something below it that looks like this. [code]        if (i == 15007) {
           class8.aStringArray189 = new String[5];
           class8.aStringArray189[1] = "Wear";
           class8.anIntArray156 = new int[2];
           class8.anIntArray160 = new int[2];
           class8.anIntArray156[0] = 10394;
           class8.anIntArray160[0] = 22463;
           class8.anIntArray156[1] = 6020;
           class8.anIntArray160[1] = 6020;
           class8.anInt174 = 6583;
           class8.anInt181 = 860;
           class8.anInt190 = 2012;
           class8.anInt198 = 188;
           class8.anInt204 = 0;
           class8.anInt169 = 17;
           class8.anInt194 = 0;
           class8.anInt165 = 6653;
           class8.anInt200 = 6687;
           class8.anInt188 = -1;
           class8.anInt164 = -1;
           class8.anInt175 = 6570;
           class8.anInt197 = 6575;
           class8.aString170 = "Green Helm";
           class8.aByteArray178 = "It's a Green helm".getBytes();
                }[/code]

4.) Where it says [code]class8.anIntArray156 = new int[2];
           class8.anIntArray160 = new int[2];
           class8.anIntArray156[0] = 10394;
           class8.anIntArray160[0] = 22463;
           class8.anIntArray156[1] = 6020;
           class8.anIntArray160[1] = 6020;[/code]


5.) Array156 is the original colors and Array160 are the new colors.

6.) Where it says [code]class8.anInt165 = 6653;
           class8.anInt200 = 6687;[/code] These are the male and female wearing ids

7.) [code]class8.anInt174 = 6583;[/code] This is the drop and inventory model

8.) [code]class8.aString170 = "Green Helm";[/code]  and  [code]class8.aByteArray178 = "It's a Green helm".getBytes();[/code] are pretty much self explanatory. [Item Name and Examine info].

9.)  This is pretty much the basics. If Your new at this stuff i recommend messing around with the codes like i    did when i first started recoloring

10.) I recommend finding a item dump if i find mine i will post it, it has some original colors in it.
